Field Report Pro is designed to assist law enforcement personnel in documenting incidents and generating structured field notes.

⸻

Data Collection
Field Report Pro does not collect, transmit, or store user data on external servers. All information entered into the app remains on the user’s device unless the user chooses to share or export that information.

⸻

Data Usage
Information entered into the app is used solely for generating structured notes and narratives. The app does not access, transmit, or share user data.

⸻

Third-Party Services
Field Report Pro does not use third-party analytics, tracking tools, or cloud-based services.

⸻

User Responsibility
Users are solely responsible for ensuring that their use of Field Report Pro complies with all applicable laws, court rulings, CJIS requirements, and their agency’s policies and procedures. Users should exercise caution when entering, storing, or sharing sensitive or protected information.

⸻

Limitation of Liability
The developer of Field Report Pro is not responsible for any misuse of the application or for any consequences resulting from the handling, storage, or sharing of information entered into the app.

